# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: runtime
domain: organization
scope: organization.core
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for organization.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers organization visibility,
membership-aware display,
role-aware action surfaces,
state-aware rendering,
and bounded failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- organization identity must resolve
- membership scope must resolve
- actor role scope must resolve
- state scope must be valid
- boundary scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid organization identity
- invalid membership scope
- invalid role scope
- invalid state path
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish organization state,
membership state,
role context,
visibility context,
and failure surface.

## review_checklist
- runtime scope is explicit
- membership-aware rendering is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
